    <note>Wu(3) Yue [1992] Shili's [4023] son and Shiren's [4022] nephew. Yue's maternal grandfather, Wang(2) Ling [3967], was the husband of the younger sister of Wang(2) Anshi's [1762] wife, Wu(3) Shi. Wang(2) Anshi arranged the marriage because of his admiration for his scholarship. Wu(3) Shifu [4021], the son-in-law of Yang(2) Daya's [2029] (qv.) son, Hang [4042], was probably an uncle as was Wu(3) Shineng [1982]. XNYL, 21.12b, 22.9b, 34.9a, 127.3b, 168.4a;SHY:ZG, 4.14b-15a; Wang Yang, WJ, 14.13a. CBD, 2, 1119.</note>
